items.title: Video shows moments around fatal shooting of Alex Pretti in Minneapolis
items.description: Bystander footage has captured the seconds before the killing of 37-year-old Alex Pretti.

items.title: Captain of suspected Russian shadow tanker in French custody
items.description: French officials seized the tanker, named the Grinch, in the Mediterranean Sea on Thursday.

items.title: Climber Alex Honnold scales 101-floor skyscraper without safety gear
items.description: Alex Honnold has become the first person to climb the Taiwanese building alone without safety equipment.

items.title: Party backed by generals set for landslide as 'sham' Myanmar election ends
items.description: Many parties were banned and there was no voting in about half the country which is gripped by fear and civil war.

items.title: Who was Alex Pretti, the intensive care nurse shot dead in Minneapolis?
items.description: He has been described as an avid outdoorsman who loved mountain biking.
